description: PureAV Blue Series Mini-Stereo Extension Cables from Belkin allow connection of portable audio equipment with mini-stereo jacks, such as CD players, digital audio players, sound cards, headphones, and portable multimedia speakers. Simply plug in one end of this 6-foot cable to your mini-stereo audio cable and the other end to your audio component to allow longer distances between your components. The superior design ensures maximum signal transfer and reduces interference for a natural, more accurate sound.
title: Belkin PureAV Mini-Stereo Extension Cable (6 feet)
